---
title: Yoghurt and Dukkah Crusted Chicken with Aubergine and Bulgur Wheat
description: Have you heard of dukkah? It’s a delicious Egyptian condiment full of nuts, spices and herbs. We’re so inspired by our dukkah suppliers - they ONLY make dukkah, so they’re absolute experts - that we made
this dish in their honour. Voila!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/yoghurt-and-dukkah-crusted-chick-7d57d7be.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/yoghurt-and-dukkah-crusted-chick-844ff3e0.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 400 kcal
